title: (x) Francis Upritchard typewriter font - Pica 10 Pitch {Zachary Ohlman}
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/files/katecomp2_3693.jpg)

This is very similar to Prestige Elite but it’s definitely not.
author: bergh

comments.content: I think it is [Schreibmaschine EF](http://web.archive.org/web/20070125111346/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/schreibmaschine-ef-regular/) but [Pica 10 Pitch](http://web.archive.org/web/20070125111346/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/bitstream/pica-10-pitch/) is close aswell
Thanks! It’s most definitely Pica 10 Pitch.
